title: Digable Planets - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Digable Planet performing live at THING Festival at Fort Warden in Port Townsend, Washington. Recorded August 27th, 2023

Songs:
The May 4th Movement 
Where I’m From
Jettin’
Rebirth of Slick (Cool Like Dat)

Ishmael Butler “Butterfly” - Vocals
